indium requires tcl/tk and bwidget to be installed on your system

fast install guide.. 
   type as root: 
    # ./configure --prefix=/var/indimail \
        --libexecdir=/var/indimail/libexec --sysconfdir=/var/indimail/etc \
        --enable-mysqlincdir=/usr/include/mysql \
        --enable-mysqllibdir=/usr/lib/mysql \
        --mandir=/var/indimail/man --sysconfdir=/var/indimail/etc
    # make
    # make install-strip
